arista.description: The Structure of Management Information for the Arista Networks enterprise.

aristaProducts.name: aristaProducts
aristaProducts.description: aristaProducts is the root object identifier from which sysObjectID values are assigned. Values are defined in ARISTA-PRODUCTS-MIB.

aristaModules.name: aristaModules
aristaModules.description: aristaModules provides a root object identifier from which MODULE-IDENTITY values may be assigned.

aristaMibs.name: aristaMibs
aristaMibs.description: aristaMibs provides a root object identifier for management-related MIBs.

aristaExperiment.name: aristaExperiment
aristaExperiment.description: aristaExperiment provides a root object identifier for experimental MIBs. The structure of information for these MIBs can not be guaranteed between releases.
